u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4951,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/11\/quran-reciters-scribes\/","url_meta":{"origin":3063,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Reciters are with angelic scribes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe example\u00a0of one\u00a0who recites the Quran and memorizes it is that of one with the 'righteous and noble scribes'\u00a0(80:15).\u00a0The example of one who recites the Quran and is\u00a0committed\u00a0to\u00a0it, although it is difficult for him, is that of one with\u00a0a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2750,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/02\/example-recite-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":3063,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Parable of reciters of Allah&#8217;s Book","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa al-Asha'ri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe parable of the believer who recites the Quran is that of a citrus fruit, which tastes good and has a pleasant scent. The parable of the believer who does not recite the Quran is that of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41209,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/salat-after-fajr-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":3063,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salah: No voluntary prayers after Fajr and \u2018Asr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no prayer after the morning prayer until the sun has risen, and there is no prayer after the afternoon prayer until the sun has set.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 552, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 626 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/make-your-last-prayer-witr\/","url_meta":{"origin":3063,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Witr: Make last prayer at night Witr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMake the last of your prayers at night the Witr prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 998, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 751 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\